name: Options vs. Futures: Why Crypto’s Options Market Has 97% Room to Grow
description: Beneath the wet brass arches of the decaying matrix, the grotesque wardens perform their kinetic doctrine. They circle the shattered sphere, where the Market Soul sleeps—magenta and potent. A vast, latent matrix awaits the unwinding, the 97% potential glowing in the shadow of the cathedral's digital silence.
